ers, you'll go in-depth with the language and see the tricks and secrets that the Go masters are using to make their applications perform. For example, you'll learn to use Go's powerful reflection libraries and work with real-world examples of integration with C code.</p>","updatedAt":"2015-12-23T19:13:20.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"chiraggude/awesome-laravel","categoryHTML":"<h2>Podcasts</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.laravelpodcast.com/\">The Laravel Podcast</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-12-23T18:20:42.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"chiraggude/awesome-laravel","categoryHTML":"<h2>Podcasts</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://laracasts.simplecast.fm/\">The Laracasts Snippet</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-12-23T18:20:42.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"hantuzun/awesome-clojurescript","categoryHTML":"<h2>Awesome ClojureScript</h2><h3>Document Object Model</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/dubiousdavid/dominator\">Dominator</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/dubiousdavid/dominator\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">74</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":74,\"repo\":\"dubiousdavid/dominator\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> – Virtual-Dom in ClojureScript.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-12-23T14:49:14.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"hantuzun/awesome-clojurescript","categoryHTML":"<h2>Awesome ClojureScript</h2><h3>Document Object Model</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://ckirkendall.github.io/enfocus-site/\">Enfocus</a> – A DOM manipulation and templatin